{"word":"ληναῖος","slug":"ληναῖος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n62927\" key=\"lhnai=os\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ληναῖος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">α</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, (<sense id=\"n62927.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ληνός</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>) <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">belonging to the wine-press</tr_>; esp. </sense> <sense n=\"1\" id=\"n62927.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> epith. of Dionysus, as <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">god of the wine-press</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0060.tlg001.perseus-grc3:3:63\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.S.\">D.S.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.63</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n62927.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Λήναια</orth> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἱερά</foreign>), <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τά</gen>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the Lenaea</tr_>, an Athenian (also Rhodian, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12(1).125</biblScope> </bibl>) festival held in the month <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ληναιών</foreign> (i.e. Gamelion) in honour of Dionysus, at which there were dramatic contests, esp. of the Com. Poets, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1155\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ach.\">Ach.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1155</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.). </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n62927.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Λήναιον</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the Lenaeum</tr_>, the place at Athens where the Lenaea were held, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὑπὶ Ληναίῳ ἀγών</foreign> the <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Lenaean</title_> dramatic contest, opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰ κατ᾽ ἄστυ</foreign>, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg001.perseus-grc1:504\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">504</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg022:327d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Prt.\">Prt.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">327d</biblScope></bibl>, Lex ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg021.perseus-grc1:10\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.10</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Διονύσια τὰ ἐπὶ Ληναίῳ</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ SIG\">SIG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1029.9</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iv B.C.)</date>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}